Class CorpPosType

java.lang.Object
  edu.wpi.cs.jburge.SEURAT.rationaleData.CorpPosType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public final class CorpPosType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Defines an enumerated class for different positions within a corporation. These levels were based on those used at Charles River Analytics and really just serve as a placeholder for "real" levels that should match those used by the company using SEURAT. Ideally thouhg, we would want the levels to be editable/extendible - more like the constraint or argument ontology hierarchies.

burgeje
